data.description: This stunning, meticulously cared for 2869 sq ft home is located in the highly sought-after T - Bar M neighborhood. The open floorplan offers a spacious Master retreat and a beautifully updated kitchen featuring a large center island and a refrigerator/freezer seamlessly integrated into the cabinetry. In addition to the main house, there is a separate guest house complete with a kitchen, bedroom, full bath, and a garage (474 sq ft). This versatile space is perfect for accommodating family, guests, or even serving as a mother-in-law suite. The expansive backyard provides ample room for entertaining with multiple areas to gather and enjoy.
